<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_120" id="59v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l1">Claſen Dulin cʒu Meincʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l2">Lıeber her Clas / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l3">künig <expan>ſelig<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnüʒʒe / <expan>Deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewrs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbens</expan> / <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l4">ew <expan>frewntlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiʒʒe / vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> wol / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l5">einen <expan>ſünderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> güten frewnd vnd günner an ew <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l6">wir auch allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_120_line_1576569640894_1891"><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> vnd <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l7">ew cʒemal <expan>fleiʒʒıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> / Was Jr trefflıchs ervaret <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den lewffen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l8">wie ſich die nu fürbas in den <expan>dinge<ex>n</ex></expan> machen vnd <expan>anſlahe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l9">des ew dunk vns ein notdurft cʒevvıſſen / daʒ Jr vns das allweg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l10">ye <expan>alſv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> füglıch ſeÿ / cʒe wiſſen tün vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l12">vvöllet / So vvöllen den <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das lone 
<add><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l11">allcʒeit </ab></add> / <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l13"><expan>v<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>ſünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan></del> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchulden</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l15"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>vrba<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> . </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l16">Cedula </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l17">Auch haben wir dem boten das lon 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſchon </del> gerichtet / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_120" id="59v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Clasen Dulin czu Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Clas, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> künig,
                                <expan>selig<ex>er</ex></expan> gedechtnüzze,
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewrs
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibens</expan>
<expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew <expan>frewntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleizze und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> wol, daz wir einen
                                <expan>sünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> güten frewnd und günner an ew
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das wir auch allczeit
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewr
                            <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan></add>; und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew czemal
                            <expan>fleizzikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>, was ir trefflichs ervaret
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den lewffen, wie sich die nu fürbas in
                        den <expan>dinge<ex>n</ex></expan> machen und
                            <expan>anslahe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, des ew dunk uns ein notdurft cze wissen, daz
                        ir uns das allweg ye, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ew
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> füglich sey, cze wissen tün und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. So wöllen den
                                <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das lone <add>allczeit</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und das <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                                <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>sünderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i</expan>. </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula <lb/>Auch haben wir dem boten das lon gerichtet. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
